b"To recap:

\xf0\x9f\x94\xb9$1m market cap
\xf0\x9f\x94\xb9Less than 2000 wallets (holders)
\xf0\x9f\x94\xb9Little to no whales
\xf0\x9f\x94\xb9No team 'dumps' expected anymore
\xf0\x9f\x94\xb980% in circulation (15% locked long term within WeOwn validators for 34% network dominance)
\xf0\x9f\x94\xb980.2m $CHX soft locked (staked for validator rewards)"

b'https://t.co/P6lQiggs3i tells me team owned tokens mentioned above are all part of the non-circulating supply. Right now 80% of all $CHX tokens (max supply 168m, circ supply 135m) are in circulation.\n\n80m+ $CHX are staked towards public validators for rewards.'

b'1.9m $CHX in a wallet that occasionally is used to pay for public validator reward incentives. \n\nNo reason to assume they will sell off these tokens any time soon. Also no reason to assume that validator reward incentives will end, unless great utility (tx) is around the corner.'

b'7.7m $CHX are shared between 7 wallets, originally marked Unused, but my assumption is that they currently function as (remaining) team/founder wallets. \n\nTeam could decide to sell these, but again I do not think this will happen anytime soon.'

b"23.8m $CHX are locked in the WeOwn owned validators.\n\nMy assumption? They are keeping at least a 34% network share so these tokens will stay locked. They could decide to give up that 34% and sell off these tokens, but I'd say chances are slim, especially at this stage."

b"Roughly 18 months have past since this update. Let's go into current status:

1) All vested tokens were released. 
2) The reserve was used for market making, business development and marketing (EMPTY).
3) A wallet with 21.3m $CHX contains all 'non-swapped' $CHX tokens (public)"

b'69m $CHX tokens were sold to public during the initial raise. 100m $CHX tokens in the hands of WeOwn of which 45m was part of Reserve, 50m owned by team & management and 5m for ongoing operational expenses during time of TGE (I assume these 5m were used back in 2018 already).'

b"So based on this: 

https://t.co/dhjSgOhp0r

There's not much $CHX in the hands of team. Token distribution among (big) holders has balanced out as well (earliest of holders got out), check: https://t.co/T4Jblng5Pn

I am seeing glimpses of a bright future ahead (again!) https://t.co/yIxfZANIR1"
